&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chef - Part Time Hours - Saturday and Sunday 8.00 -4.30 (with a 30 minute unpaid break).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;£9.00 per hour - Based in Old Trafford, Manchester, M16 7NX.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deepdene Care is a national mental healthcare provider operating fivehomes nationwide, offering high quality care to people with severe and enduring mental health needs. It was established in 1987, providing services that include specialised nursing care, residential careand community housing, we are able to provide our service users witha support structure best suited to their individual needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We currently have some exciting opportunities and are looking for a reliable, experienced individual with a friendly and caring nature to work as a chef in Old Trafford, Manchester M16 7NX.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Pattern: Part Time Hours Saturday and Sunday 8.00am - 4.30pm.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous experience is essential and further in-house training is provided.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Duties will include planning and preparing meals for clients, adhering to health and hygiene practices and meeting dietary requirements.A responsible and caring attitude is important. You will work in friendly but sometimes challenging environments, therefore excellent interaction and communication skills are essential.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Successful applicants are required to provide an enhanced disclosure.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We can offer successful applicants benefits such as:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An opportunity to work for a company who invest in their employees and have recently celebrated 30 years of success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free DBS check&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refer a friend fee&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pension scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-house Training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee Assistance programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deepdene Care Contract of Employment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If this appeals to you, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please ensure you complete the application form in full. Partially complete forms will not be accepted.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We reserve the right to withdraw the vacancy at any time If there is a high volume of applications, therefore we would recommend that you submit your application as early as possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
